items.title: A Trump plan for TikTok is coming together — and Oracle may play a starring role
items.description: Chinese tech giant ByteDance has roughly two weeks to save its video app TikTok from a renewed US ban — and there are signs cloud computing giant Oracle may play a prominent role.
